rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0001
rows.name:
We discussing how Invidia was able to
develop as country.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Invidia recently seen rapid growth
in development of country thanks
to certain someone.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0003
rows.name:
We analyze from different angles and
find purchase of products not the only
key factor in growth of development.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0004
rows.name: First point is helping people in distress.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0005
rows.name:
Solving of problems lead to brighter
and more certain future. This factor
number one.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0007
rows.name:
Fulfilling mercenary requests mean
improvement of quality of life on
both personal and state level.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0009
rows.name:
Communication on personal level
seem to be main reason for effective
information network.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0010
rows.name:
And lastly, discovery of uncharted
regions.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0011
rows.name:
When new location discovered, news
of discovery travel fast.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0012
rows.name:
That give rise to new supply of
resources, which supplement country
growth.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0013
rows.name:
...And that basically summarize reasons
for success of Invidia.

rows.label: tlk42350143_03_msg0014
rows.name:
Whew... Long explanation make
Kurolo sleepy. Please not to ask
Kurolo to explain more...
